nodes.text: 2163 was an OOM command battle droid that served within the Droid Army of the Trade Federation Invasion of Naboo. In 32 BBY, he attempted to stop Qui-Gon Jinn and Queen Amidala from going to Coruscant, but ended up being bisected by the Jedi instead alongside 1933 and 7169. His death was in vain, as Jinn ended up eventually going to Coruscant.

2163 appeared in 1999 with the release of the Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace film. Similar to all other battle droids in the film, 2163's designation was printed on its back. The command battle droid was voiced by Peter Serafinowicz, the actor who also dubbed the Sith Lord Darth Maul's voice in the film.
